titleNullable: HPA - Train Data With Additional Metadata
subtitleNullable: CSV File for Meta-Data of Train Dataset & Cell Segmentation Masks and BBoxes
descriptionNullable:
This is the Train CSV file after running the CellSegmentator tool on the images and recording relevant outputs.

**The extra data included is:**

- RLE Masks (for each cell)
- Bounding Boxes (for each cell)
- Image Width
- Image Height
